						<div>
							<h6><strong>Sales: +2347098856784</strong></h6>
							<p>Lines open between 8am and 7pm Monday - Sunday</p>
						</div>
						<div>
							<h6><strong>Technical: +234704885584</strong></h6>
							<p>Lines open between 8am and 7pm Monday - Sunday</p>
						</div>
						<h4 class="header-height"><i class="ft-mail"></i> E-mail us at:</h4>
						<div>
							<h6><strong>Sales: support@nhp.gov.ng</strong></h6>
							<p>We respond to your emails within 15mins</p>
						</div>
						<div>
							<h6><strong>Technical: support@nhp.gov.ng</strong></h6>
							<p>We respond to your emails within 15mins</p>
						</div>
						<h4 class="header-height"><i class="ft-map-pin"></i> Find us at:</h4>
						<div>
